snippet.title: Amber Heard & Johnny Depp:  The Real ABUSER FINALLY REVEALED!! (UNCENSORED AUDIO!)
snippet.description:
#JusticeForJohnnyDepp #amberheard #metoo #timesup

Hey everyone!  Welcome back.  I'll keep this description short.  This is a recorded conversation/argument between Johnny Depp and Amber Heard.  This was recorded just months before they filed for divorce in May 2016.

I know this is a long one, but I encourage you to listen to/watch the entire video.  I feel this finally confirms who the real abuser was in this relationship, and the audio speaks for itself, although I do add some context and insight...but try to keep it to minimum. (Time stamps below)

Amber Admitted to previously hitting Johnny (Video):
https://youtu.be/PbXTr41ZFTQ

Amber Speaking at Women's March (Speech begins at 3:02:12)
https://youtu.be/SmO8Wh0f8tc

Twitter: @ThatBrianFella

I understand there are some who don't like me interrupting the audio to add context or insight. Here are some time stamps that might help.
